message.body: Its Kristen's husband Casey. Looking for a good place in San Jose for dinner tonight. Any suggestions?
hi casey, what type of food you looking for? This place has a lot of options. All walking distance once you park. http://www.santanarow.com/dining/
I am open to anything, just like good food.
http://www.originaljoes.com/ this place is good if you near downtown.
also the steakhouse at the Double Tree is actually really good.
Cool thanks. Ate here last night was good. Thanks for the help and see you tomorrow
see you tomorrow. http://www.yelp.com/biz/henrys-world-famous-hi-life-san-jose this place is good too.
